page.title: 18THE OLD RAILWAY
page.content: The railway was closed in 1970 by Dr.Beeching and is now overgrown and makes a lovely nature reserve.It was the main East coast line to London and was closed from Spalding to Grimsby.There are plans to build a road along it to relieve the A16.Here is a list to show the plants and flowers found along the line from Algarkirk to the old station where an Agricultural firm now does its business.{ {NETTLE,STONECROP,WHITECLOVER,DAISY, } {WHITE DEAD NETTLE,PINEAPPLE WEED {IVY,TREFOIL,SPEAR THISTLE,DOG DAISY, {RED CLOVER,SILVER WEED,CHICKWEED, {MARE'S TAIL,SOW THISTLE,WILD ROSE, {DANDELION,FAT HEN,DOCKIN,PLANTAIN, THERE ARE MANY MORE.HERE ARE SOME CREATURES THAT WE FOUND.{BUTTERFLY, {CATERPILLARS,RABBIT,SNAIL,BEE, {RED BEETLE,MOTHS,GNATS,GRASSHOPPER.
